99-0630 (La. 4/23/99)

Walter SPINKS v. JAMES HUTCHINS FARMS. No. 99-C-0630. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: James Hutchins Farms; Hutchins, James Farms; Employers Insurance/Wausau; — Defendant(s); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Office of Workers Compensation District IE Number 97-04845; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CA98 0811

Denied.

KIMBALL and VICTORY, JJ. would grant the writ. KNOLL, J. not on panel.
